dct_title_s: Ville de Paris plan des servitudes
dct_description_sm: Map shows easements for the protection of existing sites and existing prospects or those to be created; historic and archaeological protection easements; scheduled architectural easements; controlled architectural easements; and open [outdoor] spaces to be protected. Some sites shown pictorially.
dct_creator_sm: Seine (France). Préfecture. Services techniques de topographie et d'urbanisme
